snippet.title: Circuit Breakers | Gameplay Dev Diary | PS4
snippet.description:
Circuit Breakers is a hectic, top-down shooter that brings back couch co-op to the PS4. Releasing in early 2017. Will you be ready to #ShootAllRobots?

Follow Circuit Breakers on Twitter: https://twitter.com/ShootAllRobots

Like Circuit Breakers on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/Circuit-Breakers-661312577379842/?fref=ts
